@startuml

actor User
participant System
database DB

== Anonymous Mode ==
User -> System: Build a schedule
note right of User: No account needed,\nCalendar is session only.
User -> System: Prompted to sign up to save

alt Signs up
    System -> DB: Save calendar to new account
else Declines
    System -> User: Calendar discarded on exit
end

== Authenticated Mode ==
User -> System: Sign up or log in
System -> User: Account created or session resumed
User -> System: Create a calendar
User -> System: Select a program and semester
System -> User: Load prospectus\n(advisory only - terms, year standing)

loop Building schedule
    User -> System: Add or remove a section
    System -> System: Evaluate rules\n(prerequisites, corequisites,\nunit cap, minimum year standing, etc...)
    alt Issues found
        System -> User: Display non-blocking warnings\n(user may proceed anyway)
    end
end

User -> System: Save calendar
System -> DB: Store calendar to account

@enduml
